        <article class="post">
            <strong class="kicker"><a href="/posts/chart/">Charts</a></strong>
            
            <h1>Visualizing the Impact of Mega-Storms on Transit</h1>
            <ul class="meta">
                <li><a href="/authors/emily-badger/" title="Emily Badger">Emily Badger</a></li>
                <li>May 22, 2013</li>
                <li><a href="#disqus_thread"  data-disqus-identifier="post_5660" class="link-comments">Comments</a></li>
